According to the document, WeWork's revenue for the six months ended June 30, 2021 was **$1,191,331 thousand (or approximately $1.19 billion)**.

This information can be found in the "SELECTED HISTORICAL FINANCIAL INFORMATION OF WEWORK" section under "Consolidated Statements of Operations Data."
